<div
  class="modal fade"
  id="cancelBenefit"
  aria-labelledby="cancelBenefitLabel"
  tabindex="-1"
  role="dialog"
>
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <h2
        class="h3 text-secondary subTitleDecoration mb-3"
        id="cancelBenefitLabel"
      >
        Vyhrajte iPhone 15 PRO Vyhrajte iPhone 15 PRO
      </h2>
      <div class="questionnairesCount">1/2</div>
      <button
        type="button"
        class="close"
        data-bs-dismiss="modal"
        aria-label="Close"
      ></button>

      <p class="fw-light mb-32">
        Odpovězte správně na soutěžní, otázku a vyhrajte svelé ceny! Výherce se
        losuje 20.11.2024.
      </p>
      <p class="modal__perex">
        Jaký byl průměrný počet fanoušků na zápasech Sparty v sezóně 2023/2024 v
        domovské O2 areně?
      </p>
      <div class="radio-group">
        <label class="radio-wrapper">
          <input type="checkbox" name="answer[]" value="A" />
          <span class="radio-label">
            <span class="radio-letter">A</span>
            <span class="radio-text">11 586</span>
          </span>
        </label>
        <label class="radio-wrapper">
          <input type="checkbox" name="answer[]" value="B" />
          <span class="radio-label">
            <span class="radio-letter">B</span>
            <span class="radio-text">12 158</span>
          </span>
        </label>
        <label class="radio-wrapper">
          <input type="checkbox" name="answer[]" value="C" />
          <span class="radio-label">
            <span class="radio-letter">C</span>
            <span class="radio-text">13 268</span>
          </span>
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          data-bs-target="#cancelBenefit2"
          data-bs-toggle="modal"
        >
          Další
        </button>
        <button data-bs-dismiss="modal" class="btn btn-secondary closeModal">
          Zrušit
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div
  class="modal fade"
  id="cancelBenefit2"
  aria-labelledby="cancelBenefitLabel2"
